data.description:
**Pre-Foreclosure** Opportunity for a home in pretty good shape! This 3 Bedroom, Single Story Seamist Model is nestled on a very private lot and a cul-de-sac street in the 55+ age community of Palm Shores at Gables End. New Roof installed in 2018 and a great floorplan! 2 Car Garage! Community amenities include PICKLEBALL, Tennis, Pool and more! This is a ''MUST SEE and Priced to Sell FAST!''Photos are Virtually Staged. Palm Shores is situated in Boynton Beach, located in beautiful Palm Beach County. It is ideally located close to I-95, the Florida Turnpike, and the West Palm Beach & Fort Lauderdale Airports. The Boynton Beach area offers its residents year round sub-tropical weather, an abundance of shopping, hundreds of restaurants, gorgeous beaches, world class golf courses and is so centrally located that it's the perfect place to call home.

The Palm Shores community is comprised of two hundred & twenty-two one family homes and boasts three beautiful lakes with a one mile walking path.  The Clubhouse features a multi-purpose "Palm Room"  which includes a kitchen, stage & dance  floor.  There is also a fitness room and sauna, a library, ping-pong & billiard rooms.   Outdoor amenities include a temperature controlled pool & hot tub, BBQ grill, shuffleboard courts, pickle ball & tennis courts.
